  "text": "Motivated by the continual development of new PageRank-based algorithms and analysis of Dirichlet eigenvectors in [CITATION_1] , we develop and analyze Dirichlet PageRank algorithms. For a connected graph G, we examine a Dirichlet PageRank equation and compute the unique solution with Dirichlet boundary conditions pr(v) = 0 for vertices v on the boundary of a specified vertex subset S.",
